   &UR; KOSOVO (Moved in ``i'' category) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   KOSOVO-ALBANIA (Kukes, Albania) _ Refugees pouring into Albania
from Kosovo have been bringing with them detailed firsthand
accounts of mass killings and burned corpses. The reports have been
so frequent and so repetitive in their detail that officials have
brought in 60 specially trained investigators to interview refugees
and keep records for possible war-crimes indictments. By John
Kifner.
</P>
