United States are down. &QL; 
 &UR; By Kim Severson &QL;  &LR; 
 &UR; c. 1999 The San Francisco Chronicle &QL;  &LR; 
 &QL; 
Petaluma, Calif. _ &UR; CLASSIC-Cheese &LR;  _ When you're deep in cows, you
might as well make cheese. Marin French Cheese Co. makes its four
