51 points, or half a percent, and the Nasdaq index was off 4
points, or 0.1 percent. Elsewhere, prices rose 0.9 percent in
Tokyo, while the Hong Kong market remained closed. Shares rose 1.4
percent in Frankfurt, 1.6 percent in London, 0.9 percent in Brazil
and 1.4 percent in Mexico. On the American debt market, the long
bond was up 15/32 point. By Kenneth N. Gilpin.
