INDECISIVE-WOMAN (Los Angeles) _ Mary Lord, who admits she flipped
a coin to decide whether to get married, wins the dubious title of
Least Decisive Person in America. Has sidebar slugged
Indecision-Tips. By Carol Bidwell. (Also moving on ``a'' nation and
``n'' state new wires).
<TEXT>
<P>
   &QL; 
INDECISION-TIPS (Los Angeles) _ How to get past indecision. By
Carol Bidwell. (Also moving on ``a'' nation and ``n'' state new
wires). &QL;
</P>
</TEXT>
