<DOCNO> NYT19990406.0151 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-04-06 15:43 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7839 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-HUGH-HEFNER-LADN     04-06 1373
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-HUGH-HEFNER-LADN </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
HEFNER BACK TO BEING A PLAYBOY
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients)  
(Also moving in ``l'' lifestyle news file)  
By DAVID BLOOM  
 c.1999 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
<P>
