<P>
   US-KOSOVO (Washington) _ President Clinton rejects Yugoslav
President Slobodan Milosevic's call for a five-day cease-fire to
mark the Orthodox Christian Easter. Clinton takes steps to cement
allied unity behind NATO's goal of forcing the immediate Yugoslav
withdrawal from Kosovo so that refugees can return there under
allied protection. By STEWART M. POWELL.
</P>
