<P>
   TART SMARTS: Savory tarts are a supreme way to celebrate spring.
And tarts _ or tortas _ are so versatile, you can tinker with most
recipes to include your favorite vegetables, cheeses and meats.
Sliced thin and small, they work well as appetizers or side dishes.
Make heartier cuts and pair with a salad for a main meal. (Includes
one 4-column color photo of a tart.)
</P>
<P>
   WITH: RECIPES: Pasta Frolla, Mushroom Tart
</P>
<P>
   WITH: CYBERSPICE: A good way to get the most out of a precious
springtime energy surge is to direct it at one project where it
will do the most good. But what to choose when so much around a
winter-weary house needs rejuvenation? The Internet has dozens of
professional kitchen organizers and experts to take you step by
painless step through a process that will continue to reap benefits
throughout the year.
</P>
<P>
   WITH: FOOD NOTES: A new study shows brown bread is tied to good
health.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; WHEELS &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   PAGE INCLUDES FOUR COLOR PHOTOGRAPHS
</P>
<P>
   BMW's M COUPE: The new M Coupe is so different from anything
else BMW has built in recent years and still so new that it's got
an astronomical quotient for inviting questions and thumbs-up
gestures. It's not a car for those times when you want to be
ignored. (Includes 4-column color photograph of car's exterior,
1-column color photo of interior and 1-column photo of M Coupe's
logo.)
</P>
<P>
   WITH: AT A GLANCE: Fact box previewing the BMW M Coupe.
</P>
<P>
