laptop computer knows even the lightest machine becomes a
heavyweight over time. So it was with some concern that I began
searching for portable options for my son to use for writing at
home and school. While cruising Web sites about technology and
learning, I discovered the AlphaSmart keyboard. I'm glad I did.
(Includes 1-column B&AMP;W photo of keyboard)
