anything else BMW has built in recent years and still so new that
it's got an astronomical quotient for inviting questions and
thumbs-up gestures. It's not a car for those times when you want to
be ignored. (DeVault, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) Includes 4
column color photograph of car's exterior, a 1-column color photo
of interior and 1-column photo of M Coupe's logo.
