<HEADLINE>
US SEES `PLOY' IN MILOSEVIC CEASE-FIRE OFFER 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  
 By ANN SCALES  
 c.1999 The Boston Globe  
 
<TEXT>
